{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, a school of-- outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I passed that one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And suddenly, I didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I turned back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had a friend of mine who was living outside the ghetto not far from the post office, because some officers were quartered in their place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I go there to knock on-- I started to knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody answered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knock again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody answered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly, I see a German policeman and two locals are walking on the main street turning toward the post office.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I figure they're going to come there anyhow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I started to go towards them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they started, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I am going to exchange stamps to-- for-- with the Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't-- I should have mentioned that before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One day there was a hanging supposedly of partisans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I am there watching the big occasion, hanging of people, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And next there was still the German, what you would call a Master Sergeant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was looking too, and I was looking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had stamps on me, a little booklet of stamps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I kind of took it out as if I'm looking at the stamps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really wanted to see-- to get his attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe he's a stamp collector or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sure enough, he was a stamp collector.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And start saying, oh, Briefmarkensammeln, stamp collector.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I started to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, yeah, he's interested in stamp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I showed him some of the stamps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I made contact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was already in must have been October, a good month before this November 14.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went already to him a few times.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
